{"title":"Hiplok 1000 Bike Locks Go Super Secure with World’s First Anti-Angle Grinder Anchors","link":"https://bikerumor.com/hiplok-1000-anti-grinder-bike-lock-floor-anchor/","date":1699641846000,"content":"<p><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Hiplok-1000-Series-anti-angle-grinder-ebike-eMTB-bike-lock-and-wall-or-floor-anchor.jpg\" alt=\"Hiplok 1000 Series anti-theft angle-grinder-resistant bike locks &amp; wall/floor anchors for eMTB\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Hiplok-1000-Series-anti-angle-grinder-ebike-eMTB-bike-lock-and-wall-or-floor-anchor.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Hiplok-1000-Series-anti-angle-grinder-ebike-eMTB-bike-lock-and-wall-or-floor-anchor-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Hiplok-1000-Series-anti-angle-grinder-ebike-eMTB-bike-lock-and-wall-or-floor-anchor-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Hiplok-1000-Series-anti-angle-grinder-ebike-eMTB-bike-lock-and-wall-or-floor-anchor-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Hiplok-1000-Series-anti-angle-grinder-ebike-eMTB-bike-lock-and-wall-or-floor-anchor-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Hiplok-1000-Series-anti-angle-grinder-ebike-eMTB-bike-lock-and-wall-or-floor-anchor-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Hiplok-1000-Series-anti-angle-grinder-ebike-eMTB-bike-lock-and-wall-or-floor-anchor-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></p>\n<p>A newly expanded Hiplok 100 Series extends proven tamper-resistant theft protection for bikes, ebikes &amp; motorcycles combining their top-tier U-lock construction with a new ultra-secure anchor into floor or wall. Calling them the “<em>future of motorcycle &amp; bike security</em>“, these world’s first anti-angle grinder anchors adopt graphene composite tech of the separate D1000 bike lock to make it difficult for thieves to escape with your 2-wheeled pride &amp; joy…</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Hiplok anti-grinder 1000 Series Bike Lock &amp; Floor/Wall Anchors</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><div>\n\n</div></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Hiplok launching a full 1000 Series of bike/moto security leverages the success of the angle grinder resistant <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/hiplok-d1000-angle-grinder-proof-bike-lock/\" target=\"_blank\">D1000 U-lock</a> that they debuted  2 years ago. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>There are 3 new products in the Hiplok 1000 Series. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Hiplok-1000-Series-bike-lock-anchors.jpg\"><img width=\"1200\" height=\"600\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Hiplok-1000-Series-bike-lock-anchors.jpg\" alt=\"Hiplok 1000 Series anti-theft angle-grinder-resistant bike locks &amp; wall/floor anchors\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Hiplok-1000-Series-bike-lock-anchors.jpg 1200w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Hiplok-1000-Series-bike-lock-anchors-297x149.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Hiplok-1000-Series-bike-lock-anchors-800x400.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Hiplok-1000-Series-bike-lock-anchors-120x60.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Hiplok-1000-Series-bike-lock-anchors-768x384.jpg 768w\" /></a><figcaption>(Photos/Hiplok)</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<ol>\n<li>The new DX1000 is a longer shackle U-lock (210x112mm inside) designed for bigger ebikes, eMTBs, and motorcycles. Recommended Retail Price £300 / $350 / 350€. </li>\n\n\n\n<li>Combine that with a short 100mm long A1000 anchor. And then, secure into a solid wall and can rotate 360° to attach the U-lock. RRP £200 / $250 / 225€ </li>\n\n\n\n<li>Or pick the longer (430mm overall) AX1000 anchor that adds an extended bar for greater reach, secured to the floor or a wall. RRP £350 / $450 / 400€ </li>\n</ol>\n\n\n\n<p>And then, all of that gets the Sold Secure Powered Cycle Diamond and ART 4 Star rated. That then makes this about as secure a setup as you’ll find anywhere.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>(<em>Eds.: Hiplok thinks it’s more D-shaped than U-shaped. But we still feel like we’ve been calling these U-locks for decades.</em>)</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>How does it work?</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Hiplok-1000-Series-anti-angle-grinder-ebike-eMTB-bike-lock-and-wall-or-floor-anchor_trying-to-grind-it.jpg\"><img width=\"1800\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Hiplok-1000-Series-anti-angle-grinder-ebike-eMTB-bike-lock-and-wall-or-floor-anchor_trying-to-grind-it.jpg\" alt=\"Hiplok 1000 Series anti-theft angle-grinder-resistant bike locks &amp; wall/floor anchors, trying to cut\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Hiplok-1000-Series-anti-angle-grinder-ebike-eMTB-bike-lock-and-wall-or-floor-anchor_trying-to-grind-it.jpg 1800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Hiplok-1000-Series-anti-angle-grinder-ebike-eMTB-bike-lock-and-wall-or-floor-anchor_trying-to-grind-it-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Hiplok-1000-Series-anti-angle-grinder-ebike-eMTB-bike-lock-and-wall-or-floor-anchor_trying-to-grind-it-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Hiplok-1000-Series-anti-angle-grinder-ebike-eMTB-bike-lock-and-wall-or-floor-anchor_trying-to-grind-it-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Hiplok-1000-Series-anti-angle-grinder-ebike-eMTB-bike-lock-and-wall-or-floor-anchor_trying-to-grind-it-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Hiplok-1000-Series-anti-angle-grinder-ebike-eMTB-bike-lock-and-wall-or-floor-anchor_trying-to-grind-it-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Hiplok-1000-Series-anti-angle-grinder-ebike-eMTB-bike-lock-and-wall-or-floor-anchor_trying-to-grind-it-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Hiplok’s 1000 Series lock secret is multi-material construction.  That is to say, a square 20mm hardened steel core is topped off with a ‘Ferosafe’ material – a  graphene-reinforced ceramic composite covering. Designed to burn out a dozen rotary blades and the motor of the grinder spinning them.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Hiplok-1000-Series-anti-angle-grinder-ebike-eMTB-bike-lock-and-wall-or-floor-anchor_failed-attack-after-being-cut.jpg\"><img width=\"1800\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Hiplok-1000-Series-anti-angle-grinder-ebike-eMTB-bike-lock-and-wall-or-floor-anchor_failed-attack-after-being-cut.jpg\" alt=\"Hiplok 1000 Series anti-theft angle-grinder-resistant bike locks &amp; wall/floor anchors, after atrack\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Hiplok-1000-Series-anti-angle-grinder-ebike-eMTB-bike-lock-and-wall-or-floor-anchor_failed-attack-after-being-cut.jpg 1800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Hiplok-1000-Series-anti-angle-grinder-ebike-eMTB-bike-lock-and-wall-or-floor-anchor_failed-attack-after-being-cut-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Hiplok-1000-Series-anti-angle-grinder-ebike-eMTB-bike-lock-and-wall-or-floor-anchor_failed-attack-after-being-cut-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Hiplok-1000-Series-anti-angle-grinder-ebike-eMTB-bike-lock-and-wall-or-floor-anchor_failed-attack-after-being-cut-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Hiplok-1000-Series-anti-angle-grinder-ebike-eMTB-bike-lock-and-wall-or-floor-anchor_failed-attack-after-being-cut-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Hiplok-1000-Series-anti-angle-grinder-ebike-eMTB-bike-lock-and-wall-or-floor-anchor_failed-attack-after-being-cut-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Hiplok-1000-Series-anti-angle-grinder-ebike-eMTB-bike-lock-and-wall-or-floor-anchor_failed-attack-after-being-cut-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<blockquote>\n<p>“Security is only as strong as the weakest link, which is why we’ve developed a complete anti-angle grinder security system to protect your prized possessions. Building on our proven track record in launching the first anti-angle grinder bike lock, we’re excited to launch 1000 Series, the ultimate modular security solution with graphene composite material technology at its core, for wherever you ride or store your motorcycle or bike.”</p>\n<cite><em>– Ben Smith, Hiplok Co-Founder</em></cite></blockquote>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Hiplok-1000-Series-anti-angle-grinder-ebike-eMTB-bike-lock-and-wall-or-floor-anchor_commuter-ebike-locked.jpg\"><img width=\"1800\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Hiplok-1000-Series-anti-angle-grinder-ebike-eMTB-bike-lock-and-wall-or-floor-anchor_commuter-ebike-locked.jpg\" alt=\"Hiplok 1000 Series anti-theft angle-grinder-resistant bike locks &amp; wall/floor anchors, citty ebike\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Hiplok-1000-Series-anti-angle-grinder-ebike-eMTB-bike-lock-and-wall-or-floor-anchor_commuter-ebike-locked.jpg 1800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Hiplok-1000-Series-anti-angle-grinder-ebike-eMTB-bike-lock-and-wall-or-floor-anchor_commuter-ebike-locked-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Hiplok-1000-Series-anti-angle-grinder-ebike-eMTB-bike-lock-and-wall-or-floor-anchor_commuter-ebike-locked-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Hiplok-1000-Series-anti-angle-grinder-ebike-eMTB-bike-lock-and-wall-or-floor-anchor_commuter-ebike-locked-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Hiplok-1000-Series-anti-angle-grinder-ebike-eMTB-bike-lock-and-wall-or-floor-anchor_commuter-ebike-locked-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Hiplok-1000-Series-anti-angle-grinder-ebike-eMTB-bike-lock-and-wall-or-floor-anchor_commuter-ebike-locked-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Hiplok-1000-Series-anti-angle-grinder-ebike-eMTB-bike-lock-and-wall-or-floor-anchor_commuter-ebike-locked-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>On top of that, Hiplok guarantees the 1000 Series for life.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Hiplok 1000 Series Locks – Pricing, Options &amp; Availability</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Hiplok-1000-Series-anti-angle-grinder-ebike-eMTB-bike-lock-_buy-a-D1000-now.jpg\"><img width=\"1800\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Hiplok-1000-Series-anti-angle-grinder-ebike-eMTB-bike-lock-_buy-a-D1000-now.jpg\" alt=\"Hiplok 1000 Series anti-theft angle-grinder-resistant bike locks &amp; wall/floor anchors, U-lock available now\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Hiplok-1000-Series-anti-angle-grinder-ebike-eMTB-bike-lock-_buy-a-D1000-now.jpg 1800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Hiplok-1000-Series-anti-angle-grinder-ebike-eMTB-bike-lock-_buy-a-D1000-now-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Hiplok-1000-Series-anti-angle-grinder-ebike-eMTB-bike-lock-_buy-a-D1000-now-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Hiplok-1000-Series-anti-angle-grinder-ebike-eMTB-bike-lock-_buy-a-D1000-now-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Hiplok-1000-Series-anti-angle-grinder-ebike-eMTB-bike-lock-_buy-a-D1000-now-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Hiplok-1000-Series-anti-angle-grinder-ebike-eMTB-bike-lock-_buy-a-D1000-now-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Hiplok-1000-Series-anti-angle-grinder-ebike-eMTB-bike-lock-_buy-a-D1000-now-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The new Hiplok 1000 Series of bike locks is only available as a complete set now as a pre-order. So, get one through their <a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/airlok/hiplok-1000-series-anti-angle-grinder-security-system?ref=d51zxc&amp;token=20882be7\" target=\"_blank\">Kickstarter campaign</a> for the next 3 weeks. On the other hand, the original &amp; slightly shorter Hiplok D1000 that formed the basis of the locking portion of this new 1000 Series setup is already available for 280€, with a 155x92mm internal locking area.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Hiplok-1000-Series-anti-angle-grinder-ebike-eMTB-bike-lock-and-wall-or-floor-anchor_Kickstarter-options.jpg\"><img width=\"2200\" height=\"1100\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Hiplok-1000-Series-anti-angle-grinder-ebike-eMTB-bike-lock-and-wall-or-floor-anchor_Kickstarter-options.jpg\" alt=\"Hiplok 1000 Series anti-theft angle-grinder-resistant bike locks &amp; wall/floor anchors, Kickstarter rewards\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Hiplok-1000-Series-anti-angle-grinder-ebike-eMTB-bike-lock-and-wall-or-floor-anchor_Kickstarter-options.jpg 2200w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Hiplok-1000-Series-anti-angle-grinder-ebike-eMTB-bike-lock-and-wall-or-floor-anchor_Kickstarter-options-297x149.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Hiplok-1000-Series-anti-angle-grinder-ebike-eMTB-bike-lock-and-wall-or-floor-anchor_Kickstarter-options-800x400.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Hiplok-1000-Series-anti-angle-grinder-ebike-eMTB-bike-lock-and-wall-or-floor-anchor_Kickstarter-options-120x60.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Hiplok-1000-Series-anti-angle-grinder-ebike-eMTB-bike-lock-and-wall-or-floor-anchor_Kickstarter-options-768x384.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Hiplok-1000-Series-anti-angle-grinder-ebike-eMTB-bike-lock-and-wall-or-floor-anchor_Kickstarter-options-1536x768.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Hiplok-1000-Series-anti-angle-grinder-ebike-eMTB-bike-lock-and-wall-or-floor-anchor_Kickstarter-options-2048x1024.jpg 2048w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Via Kickstarter pre-order deals, you can get the new longer DX1000 U-lock for £210 (~$257). Or the full-length AX1000 anchor on its own from £245 (~$300). Two lock + anchor bundles are also available. For £315 (~$386) you get the Compact Bundle of the DX1000 &amp; just the A1000 loop you secure to the wall or floor. And from £420 (~$514) you pick the Ultimate Bundle that combines the new long U-lock and the full-length AX1000 wall/floor anchor.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Hiplok-1000-Series-anti-angle-grinder-ebike-eMTB-bike-lock-and-wall-or-floor-anchor_eMTB-bolted-to-the-floor.jpg\"><img width=\"1800\" height=\"1080\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Hiplok-1000-Series-anti-angle-grinder-ebike-eMTB-bike-lock-and-wall-or-floor-anchor_eMTB-bolted-to-the-floor.jpg\" alt=\"Hiplok 1000 Series anti-theft angle-grinder-resistant bike locks &amp; wall/floor anchors, eMTB bolted to the floor\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Hiplok-1000-Series-anti-angle-grinder-ebike-eMTB-bike-lock-and-wall-or-floor-anchor_eMTB-bolted-to-the-floor.jpg 1800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Hiplok-1000-Series-anti-angle-grinder-ebike-eMTB-bike-lock-and-wall-or-floor-anchor_eMTB-bolted-to-the-floor-297x178.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Hiplok-1000-Series-anti-angle-grinder-ebike-eMTB-bike-lock-and-wall-or-floor-anchor_eMTB-bolted-to-the-floor-800x480.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Hiplok-1000-Series-anti-angle-grinder-ebike-eMTB-bike-lock-and-wall-or-floor-anchor_eMTB-bolted-to-the-floor-120x72.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Hiplok-1000-Series-anti-angle-grinder-ebike-eMTB-bike-lock-and-wall-or-floor-anchor_eMTB-bolted-to-the-floor-768x461.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Hiplok-1000-Series-anti-angle-grinder-ebike-eMTB-bike-lock-and-wall-or-floor-anchor_eMTB-bolted-to-the-floor-1536x922.jpg 1536w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Anyway, the crowdfunding has already more than doubled its goal. Additionally, based on previous projects, Hiplok is a pretty reliable company to pre-order with via Kickstarter. All said to save you about 30% off their anticipated future retail prices. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Pre-order now, with deliveries slater for April 2024.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.hiplok.com/1000-series\" target=\"_blank\"><em>Hiplok.com</em></a></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/hiplok-1000-anti-grinder-bike-lock-floor-anchor/\">Hiplok 1000 Bike Locks Go Super Secure with World’s First Anti-Angle Grinder Anchors</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Cory Benson","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"8a4eeaca03b383536f739456349df689d223991f9ed7de4f4aec2dd8524cbbd2","category":"Cycling"}